---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../consts";

const title = "Terms & Conditions | Hyper Digital";
const description =
  "The terms and conditions that apply to services provided by McAuliffe Holdings Limited trading as Hyper Digital.";
---
<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="bg-brand-dark text-neutral-content">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[820px] px-5 py-16 text-center sm:py-20">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl sm:text-5xl">Terms &amp; <span class="marker">conditions</span>.</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg text-neutral-content/80">
        The terms that apply when you engage Hyper Digital for work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[760px] px-5">
      <p class="text-base-content/80">
        These terms and conditions apply to all services provided by McAuliffe Holdings Limited
        trading as Hyper Digital ("Hyper Digital", "we", "us" or "our"), a New Zealand company. By
        accepting a proposal or order, you ("the Client") agree to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Acceptance and proposals</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/80">
        These terms become binding once an order is accepted. Proposals are valid for 30 days from
        the date they are issued. Any changes to an accepted proposal require our written consent.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Payment</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-base-content/80">
        <li>Invoices are due by the 20th of the month following the invoice date.</li>
        <li>Overdue balances may incur a fee of 2% per month, with a minimum of $25.</li>
        <li>Work may be paused if payment lapses.</li>
        <li>No intellectual property transfers to the Client until payment is made in full.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Changes and scheduling</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/80">
        Additional changes outside the agreed scope are billed at our hourly rate. Substantive
        changes that increase the scope of work by 15% or more require a new proposal.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Intellectual property</h2>
      <ul class="mt-2 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-base-content/80">
        <li>The Client retains ownership of any content they provide to us.</li>
        <li>Copyright in the final delivered work is assigned to the Client once payment is made in full.</li>
        <li>Preliminary works, drafts and concepts remain the property of Hyper Digital.</li>
        <li>Tools and licences used to create the work are licensed to the Client but are not transferable.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Liability and warranties</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/80">
        We provide limited warranties and exclude liability for consequential damages to the extent
        permitted by law. The Client indemnifies Hyper Digital against third-party claims arising
        from the Client's content or use of the work. Nothing in these terms limits rights under the
        Consumer Guarantees Act or other New Zealand law that cannot be excluded.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Termination</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/80">
        Either party may terminate the engagement. On termination, the Client is responsible for
        compensation covering the services rendered to that point, plus any expenses incurred.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Dispute resolution and governing law</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/80">
        These terms are governed by New Zealand law. Disputes are to be worked through by
        negotiation, then mediation, and then arbitration where required.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Privacy</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/80">
        How we handle the information you share with us is set out in
        our <a class="font-semibold text-primary" href="/privacy">privacy policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 font-display text-2xl">Contact us</h2>
      <div class="mt-2 rounded-box border border-base-300 bg-base-200 p-6">
        <p class="font-display text-lg">McAuliffe Holdings Limited t/a Hyper Digital</p>
        <p class="text-base-content/80">Napier, Hawke's Bay</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/80">
          Phone: <a class="font-semibold text-primary" href={SITE.phoneHref}>{SITE.phone}</a>
        </p>
        {SITE.email && (
          <p class="text-base-content/80">
            Email: <a class="font-semibold text-primary" href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a>
          </p>
        )}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
